'Because of one simple reason - magical energy.It is a known fact spell casters require an abundance
of mana to fight lengthy battles, no matter how powerful your spells are, or how many potions are in your
possession.Unless you are a God, your capacity for this battle will dwindle and is bound to deplete.The
truth is you need as many allies as possible to triumph in this catastrophic war.So cease making
such foolish inquiries woman and be reasonable for heavens sake.'I say, extremely frustrated and fearing I
could be killed  by the other combatants in the vicinity at any moment.'You know usually I would execute you
for speaking to me, in such a disrespectful manner although you do make a solid point.'she remarks after a short
pause.'I accept your proposal, however I do have - conditions.'


